ad6d8249","tid":2443618,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T09:45:04.000Z","msg":"控方指被告與其他黑衣人的行為，導致該兩名年輕女子合理擔心其本身安全及利益。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官劉淑嫻今裁決時指，控告並沒有傳召該兩名女子作供，主要依賴便衣警員賴展源的證供及涉案片段舉證。而該便衣警員早前供稱，他聽到相關叫囂聲由被告方向傳出、且看到被告頭部及肩部曾向前傾，故推論是被告在叫囂。裁判官則指雖然她裁定該警員可信可靠，但不接納他的部分證供，包括他推論是被告叫囂等，因涉案片段只拍攝到被告的背面、且相關叫囂聲與被告上身傾前的動作之間相隔約數秒等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E9%A3%9F%E8%82%86-%E8%8C%B6%E6%9C%A8-%E5%85%A7%E5%8F%AB%E5%8F%A3%E8%99%9F-29-%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E9%81%8A%E8%95%A9%E7%BD%AA%E4%B8%8D%E6%88%90%E7%AB%8B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E9%25A3%259F%25E8%2582%2586-%25E8%258C%25B6%25E6%259C%25A8-%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%258F%25AB%25E5%258F%25A3%25E8%2599%259F-29-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%2594%25B7%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%2595%25A9%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2588%2590%25E7%25AB%258B%2F&d=RGPktlJYpqjIeXpZRAkgw4%2FVxAEwmAwDimrVtn2syv4%3D&h=d81dfcb5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E9%25A3%259F%25E8%2582%2586-%25E8%258C%25B6%25E6%259C%25A8-%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%258F%25AB%25E5%258F%25A3%25E8%2599%259F-29-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%2594%25B7%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%2595%25A9%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2588%2590%25E7%25AB%258B%2F&h=67e97005\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E9%A3%9F%E8%82%86-%E8%8C%B6%E6%9C%A8-%E5%85%A7%E5%8F%AB%E5%8F%A3%E8%99%9F-29-%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E9%81%8A%E8%95%A9%E7%BD%AA%E4%B8%8D%E6%88%90%E7%AB%8B/</a>"},{"pid":"cbf2d39ddcebb3acabaa5a34abd94465b0d9f960","tid":2443618,"uid":32722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5772c481fd2d55960fa94c72fe93162566578be","tid":2443618,"uid":110043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T07:25:13.000Z","msg":"咁既罪都告得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T09:51:54.000Z","msg":"痴線呢D